      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. Specimens drawn from two production lots with documented dimensional inspection records. Inter-laboratory coefficient of variation for stiffness was 4.2%, confirming acceptable specimen consistency. Level 3 achieved."
