      "rationale": "ASTM F1717 compression-bending testing was conducted at a single standardized load angle and displacement rate across both laboratories. The protocol is well-established and widely accepted for regulatory submissions. Inter-laboratory reproducibility was confirmed, and all specimens were tested under identical fixturing conditions per the standard. The team considers the standardized protocol sufficient to support the intended regulatory use of the model."
