      "rationale": "Fixture geometry digitized from laboratory CAD drawings and replicated in simulation boundary conditions. Material properties matched to experimentally characterized lot. Sensitivity analysis confirmed that minor fixturing compliance differences between labs contributed less than 1.5% variation in predicted stiffness. Level 3 achieved."
